WEBVTT

00:00:19.250 --> 00:00:24.359
ظآزThe whole world is lit upظآز

00:00:24.360 --> 00:00:25.979
ظآزBecause you existظآز

00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:28.019
ظآزYou're alwaysظآز

00:00:28.020 --> 00:00:32.679
ظآزSomewhere close, flying with meظآز

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:35.299
ظآزGo to where the wind blowsظآز

00:00:35.300 --> 00:00:37.019
ظآزHold tightظآز

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:42.879
ظآزTo the ray of light that belongs to usظآز

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:47.400
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 3=

00:00:54.740 --> 00:00:57.289
You're truly dedicated
to your duty, Captain Shen.

00:00:57.290 --> 00:00:58.099
What?

00:00:58.100 --> 00:01:00.060
Are you coming
into my bedroom to protect me?

00:01:00.140 --> 00:01:01.500
I'll just wait outside

00:01:02.050 --> 00:01:03.500
to take you to the cocktail party.

00:01:08.210 --> 00:01:09.170
What's wrong?

00:01:09.410 --> 00:01:11.620
My hair seems
to be caught in the zipper,

00:01:12.580 --> 00:01:14.179
and I can't reach it.

00:01:14.180 --> 00:01:15.860
Could you come help me with it?

00:01:18.770 --> 00:01:21.260
Hurry up! The party is about to start.

00:01:21.460 --> 00:01:22.700
Captain Shen,

00:01:22.740 --> 00:01:24.340
the party is about to start.

00:01:26.020 --> 00:01:28.930
(Shen Jibai,
let's see how you handle this.)

00:01:39.540 --> 00:01:40.930
Pull it quickly.

00:01:57.940 --> 00:02:00.140
Despite Mu Zhiyu's "rich heiress" act,

00:02:00.180 --> 00:02:02.290
her romantic life is a complete blank.

00:02:02.410 --> 00:02:03.340
From here on,

00:02:03.540 --> 00:02:04.700
it's up to you.

00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:06.650
Thanks.

00:02:07.130 --> 00:02:11.410
ظآزI'm all yoursظآز

00:02:11.610 --> 00:02:16.060
ظآزAll yoursظآز

00:02:17.090 --> 00:02:18.180
Don't forget.

00:02:18.460 --> 00:02:20.679
You only get the money
if you complete the mission.

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:24.140
ظآزAll yoursظآز

00:02:24.380 --> 00:02:28.809
ظآزI'm all yoursظآز

00:02:28.810 --> 00:02:30.180
Shen Jibai,

00:02:31.770 --> 00:02:33.089
you're taking advantage of me.

00:02:33.090 --> 00:02:34.650
Don't turn this around on me.

00:02:34.980 --> 00:02:36.690
You're clearly the one
who pulled me down.

00:02:37.770 --> 00:02:42.120
ظآزAll yoursظآز

00:02:56.930 --> 00:02:58.060
Where's my earring?

00:02:59.610 --> 00:03:00.699
Did I lose it just now

00:03:00.700 --> 00:03:02.580
while I was getting dressed?

00:03:02.740 --> 00:03:04.020
Help me look for it.

00:03:06.740 --> 00:03:08.060
Where is it?

00:03:22.370 --> 00:03:23.620
(Shen Jibai,)

00:03:23.700 --> 00:03:25.690
(you fell for it. Time to slip away.)

00:03:48.370 --> 00:03:49.979
(Shen Jibai,)

00:03:49.980 --> 00:03:51.650
(you just couldn't stay away.)

00:04:00.090 --> 00:04:01.739
You're certainly dedicated.

00:04:01.740 --> 00:04:03.609
You won't even
take a chance to have a break.

00:04:03.610 --> 00:04:05.649
No wonder my stepmom
thinks so highly of you.

00:04:05.650 --> 00:04:07.049
It's truly admirable.

00:04:07.050 --> 00:04:08.809
You're truly resourceful.

00:04:08.810 --> 00:04:10.049
Just to change clothes,

00:04:10.050 --> 00:04:11.650
you used a series of schemes.

00:04:11.860 --> 00:04:13.259
With your reaction speed,

00:04:13.260 --> 00:04:14.419
it's a real shame

00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:15.460
you're not a secret agent.

00:04:15.610 --> 00:04:17.020
I don't have time for your nonsense.

00:04:17.210 --> 00:04:19.340
You're like a piece of gum
I can't shake off.

00:04:20.260 --> 00:04:23.460
Yu, why are you standing at the door
instead of going in?

00:04:28.700 --> 00:04:31.940
This must be the brute who damaged
the "Classic of Mountains and Seas."

00:04:32.090 --> 00:04:34.090
No wonder he's shouting at the entrance.

00:04:34.380 --> 00:04:36.089
I am Miss Mu's personal bodyguard,

00:04:36.090 --> 00:04:37.019
Shen Jibai.

00:04:37.020 --> 00:04:37.940
Pleasure to meet you.

00:04:40.820 --> 00:04:41.610
Right.

00:04:42.090 --> 00:04:43.820
For tonight's cocktail party,

00:04:44.020 --> 00:04:46.700
we have private collections
from our He Group.

00:04:47.090 --> 00:04:49.699
I hope you will be extra careful,
Captain Shen.

00:04:49.700 --> 00:04:50.650
Will do.

00:04:51.650 --> 00:04:53.379
Yu, Mr. Bai is waiting for us.

00:04:53.380 --> 00:04:54.580
Let's head in first.

00:04:57.410 --> 00:04:58.649
I've already checked

00:04:58.650 --> 00:04:59.800
the logo you sent me.

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:01.520
It's at the nursing home
on the outskirts of the city.

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:04.050
But whether your dad is there
still requires further investigation.

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:05.780
Don't alert them yet.

00:05:06.650 --> 00:05:07.579
Mr. Bai,

00:05:07.580 --> 00:05:08.729
let me introduce you.

00:05:08.730 --> 00:05:10.059
This is Mu Zhiyu,

00:05:10.060 --> 00:05:11.459
the heiress of Mu Group.

00:05:11.460 --> 00:05:13.900
She previously worked
at Sotheby's in the UK.

00:05:14.090 --> 00:05:14.940
Yu,

00:05:15.140 --> 00:05:16.499
this is Mr. Bai Shan.

00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:17.409
He is also one of

00:05:17.410 --> 00:05:19.260
the top collection masters
in the country.

00:05:19.620 --> 00:05:20.610
Mr. Bai,

00:05:20.650 --> 00:05:21.940
I've heard so much about you.

00:05:22.020 --> 00:05:23.649
I heard from Min

00:05:23.650 --> 00:05:25.499
that you wanted to talk to me

00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:28.220
about a partnership
for the auction of collections.

00:05:28.460 --> 00:05:29.409
I'm also

00:05:29.410 --> 00:05:30.820
very interested.

00:05:31.530 --> 00:05:32.610
But

00:05:32.650 --> 00:05:34.020
I heard

00:05:34.090 --> 00:05:36.290
that you seem to be
collaborating with Hong as well.

00:05:36.970 --> 00:05:38.259
I heard Hong

00:05:38.260 --> 00:05:39.700
has a strange temper

00:05:40.170 --> 00:05:41.769
and is full of himself.

00:05:41.770 --> 00:05:43.089
So many people went to visit him

00:05:43.090 --> 00:05:44.460
only to be turned away.

00:05:44.700 --> 00:05:46.650
They were even met with verbal abuse.

00:05:46.970 --> 00:05:48.170
Someone like him

00:05:48.410 --> 00:05:50.050
should be expelled from the art world,

00:05:51.060 --> 00:05:53.090
not to mention a partnership.

00:05:53.380 --> 00:05:54.380
Mr. Bai,

00:05:54.620 --> 00:05:55.780
I wonder

00:05:56.060 --> 00:05:57.769
if you've ever met Hong in person.

00:05:57.770 --> 00:05:58.780
No.

00:05:59.330 --> 00:06:00.529
Didn't I hear

00:06:00.530 --> 00:06:02.289
that he is impossible to meet?

00:06:02.290 --> 00:06:03.610
Forgive me for being blunt,

00:06:04.140 --> 00:06:05.169
but Hong's work

00:06:05.170 --> 00:06:06.460
speaks for itself.

00:06:06.620 --> 00:06:08.090
Putting his character aside for now,

00:06:08.500 --> 00:06:10.610
as a senior in the collection world,

00:06:10.820 --> 00:06:12.209
to try to ruin someone's career

00:06:12.210 --> 00:06:13.619
in public

00:06:13.620 --> 00:06:15.490
based solely on hearsay,

00:06:16.290 --> 00:06:17.970
don't you think that's inappropriate?

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:18.969
So you mean

00:06:18.970 --> 00:06:21.409
I am intentionally slandering him?

00:06:21.410 --> 00:06:22.220
I wouldn't dare.

00:06:23.170 --> 00:06:24.730
However, as an auctioneer,

00:06:24.770 --> 00:06:27.580
remaining impartial
is my basic professional ethic.

00:06:28.460 --> 00:06:29.649
And I cannot

00:06:29.650 --> 00:06:32.580
work with someone who defines
others based on one-sided stories.

00:06:34.330 --> 00:06:35.380
Yu,

00:06:35.500 --> 00:06:38.220
Mr. Bai was only
expressing his own view.

00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:39.459
Business is business.

00:06:39.460 --> 00:06:40.490
Let's

00:06:40.530 --> 00:06:41.579
not be impulsive.

00:06:41.580 --> 00:06:42.650
Please excuse me.

00:06:52.970 --> 00:06:53.940
Ms. Mu,

00:06:54.090 --> 00:06:54.970
this is bad.

00:06:55.430 --> 00:06:58.440
An important exhibit for this exhibition,
the Han Dynasty White Jade Bowl, is missing.

00:06:58.650 --> 00:06:59.730
Missing?

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.040
Did you check the surveillance?
Did you call the police?

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:05.329
Police? Better wait for Ms. Xu
to arrive before deciding.

00:07:05.330 --> 00:07:06.530
We can't call the police.

00:07:08.210 --> 00:07:09.170
Why?

00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:11.640
If something is lost,
we should open a case for investigation.

00:07:11.640 --> 00:07:13.579
But right now, we have no clues at all.

00:07:13.580 --> 00:07:15.440
We don't even know how it was lost.

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:17.619
Rushing to call the police
will only hurt the Mu Group's reputation

00:07:17.620 --> 00:07:20.140
and make the public
doubt our security system.

00:07:20.380 --> 00:07:21.700
Is that what you want to see?

00:07:23.130 --> 00:07:24.939
Besides, you just took over
as Business Director

00:07:24.940 --> 00:07:26.650
and something like this happens.

00:07:27.020 --> 00:07:27.969
Shouldn't you be thinking

00:07:27.970 --> 00:07:29.730
about how to handle this properly?

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:32.140
I can take responsibility
for investigating this.

00:07:32.650 --> 00:07:33.820
However,

00:07:33.850 --> 00:07:36.260
I'm afraid doing it alone
won't be enough.

00:07:37.380 --> 00:07:38.650
(Here's the chance.)

00:07:39.770 --> 00:07:40.969
Everyone in the company

00:07:40.970 --> 00:07:42.579
will fully cooperate with you.

00:07:42.580 --> 00:07:44.499
Additionally, since Jibai
is the Head of Security,

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:46.290
he's very familiar
with the security system.

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:47.379
This matter

00:07:47.380 --> 00:07:49.460
will be the joint
responsibility of both of you.

00:07:53.140 --> 00:07:55.819
(Shen Jibai, I've created
the opportunity for you.)

00:07:55.820 --> 00:07:57.940
(Don't you dare let me down.)

00:07:58.020 --> 00:08:00.340
(This woman will stop at nothing)

00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:02.650
(to achieve her goals.)

00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.170
(Stepmom,)

00:08:04.460 --> 00:08:06.220
(what kind of trick
are you trying to play now?)

00:08:13.300 --> 00:08:17.530
